                       /! my_rpg usage !\

Here you will find a short tutorial to enjoy the game

________________________________________________________________

        -> First you need to compile the code : run make

        -> to display the help menu : run ./my_rpg -h

        -> to start the game : run ./my_rpg

________________________________________________________________

You can custom the keys in the settings menu, except for the
screenshot (f2).

You can start a new game by pressing the 'NEW' button. You
also can go back to your last save by entering the resume
menu and select a save from the list.

